the night before" thing?

1:18:46.376 --> 1:18:47.757
[Woman] We can at least drink

1:18:47.792 --> 1:18:50.001
without that stupid Charlie look
of judgment.

1:18:52.831 --> 1:18:54.384
[Conversation
continues indistinctly]

1:19:05.395 --> 1:19:07.087
[Dog barking]

1:19:08.191 --> 1:19:09.503
Hmm!

1:19:13.438 --> 1:19:15.785
[Panting]

1:19:19.582 --> 1:19:22.033
So fucking stupid!

1:19:22.067 --> 1:19:24.311
So fucking stupid!
[Sobbing]

1:19:27.970 --> 1:19:30.213
[Panting]

1:19:52.649 --> 1:19:54.962
[Strains]

1:20:07.319 --> 1:20:08.976
[Grunts]

1:20:15.983 --> 1:20:17.260
[Grunts]

1:20:17.951 --> 1:20:19.953
[Panting]

1:21:08.277 --> 1:21:11.556
That glass ceiling
is a real bitch.

1:21:11.590 --> 1:21:13.489
[Echoing voice]
'I'm hoping this goes a long way

1:21:13.523 --> 1:21:16.664
'towards finally getting
that promotion.'

1:21:19.184 --> 1:21:21.048
[Sobbing]

1:21:22.670 --> 1:21:25.397
[Olivia] 'Don't be like this
on Saturday.

1:21:26.674 --> 1:21:29.091
'Absolutely perfect.'

1:21:34.441 --> 1:21:36.201
Ugh!

1:22:26.113 --> 1:22:28.495
I guess we all want
what we don't have.

1:22:28.529 --> 1:22:30.704
[Echoing voice]

1:22:37.538 --> 1:22:39.264
[Sobbing]

1:22:40.300 --> 1:22:42.336
[Echoing voices,
indistinct]

1:22:56.557 --> 1:22:58.663
[Screams]

1:23:00.734 --> 1:23:01.977
No!

1:23:24.585 --> 1:23:26.794
'The finish is perfect.'

1:23:54.546 --> 1:23:57.308
Bye, guys.
See you later.

1:24:56.298 --> 1:24:58.127
[Knocking on door]

1:24:59.439 --> 1:25:01.165
[TV blares,
knocking continues]

1:25:04.306 --> 1:25:05.928
Uh...

1:25:05.962 --> 1:25:07.343
I need help.

1:25:09.828 --> 1:25:11.727
Could I use your phone?

1:25:11.761 --> 1:25:14.143
Yeah. Wait right here,
let me grab it.

1:25:31.781 --> 1:25:33.645
[Choking]

1:26:45.579 --> 1:26:47.547
[TV blares]

1:26:50.653 --> 1:26:51.930
Mm.

1:26:56.038 --> 1:26:58.420
[Laughing]

1:29:31.089 --> 1:29:32.850
Funeral?

1:29:34.886 --> 1:29:36.163
Is she...?

1:29:37.682 --> 1:29:39.477
Don't you already know?

1:30:01.879 --> 1:30:03.605
Claire?

1:30:12.476 --> 1:30:14.063
[Church bell tolling]

1:30:15.548 --> 1:30:18.136
Hey, look. I'm not nervous,
you're nervous.

1:30:26.628 --> 1:30:28.733
Hey, Claire.

1:30:28.768 --> 1:30:31.080
Hey.

1:30:31.115 --> 1:30:33.013
Thanks for being here.

1:30:36.223 --> 1:30:38.260
Do you promise
to make her happy?

1:30:38.294 --> 1:30:41.056
What, are we practicing
my vows?

1:30:44.128 --> 1:30:46.199
Yeah, of course.

1:30:46.233 --> 1:30:48.443
Do you promise
you really see her?

1:30:50.583 --> 1:30:51.756
I do.

1:30:57.037 --> 1:30:58.073
Let me get that.

1:31:06.046 --> 1:31:07.600
Claire?

1:31:07.634 --> 1:31:09.015
Yeah, hi.

1:31:09.049 --> 1:31:10.188
Great.

1:31:10.223 --> 1:31:12.225
Olivia's right this way,
just follow me.

1:31:12.259 --> 1:31:13.847
Thanks.

1:31:13.882 --> 1:31:16.574
I wasn't sure where to go,
I've never been here before.

1:31:16.609 --> 1:31:18.956
Isn't it so beautiful?

1:31:20.302 --> 1:31:21.821
How do you know Olivia?

1:31:21.855 --> 1:31:23.788
Oh, I'm sorry.
I'm her mother.

1:31:23.823 --> 1:31:26.308
I'm... I'm Frankie.

1:31:26.342 --> 1:31:30.070
Oh, it... it's nice
to meet you.

1:31:30.105 --> 1:31:32.245
Olivia talks about you
all the time.

1:31:32.279 --> 1:31:34.489
Don't be silly.

1:31:44.015 --> 1:31:46.501
Oh, my God, Claire.

1:31:47.743 --> 1:31:50.677
Thank you so much
for coming through.

1:31:53.162 --> 1:31:55.302
It means everything.

1:31:55.337 --> 1:31:57.028
Where should I set up?

1:31:57.063 --> 1:31:59.962
- Uh, is right here OK?
- Yeah.

1:31:59.997 --> 1:32:03.794
- Uh, this is for you.
- Thank you.

1:32:03.828 --> 1:32:05.623
- I'll just be a few minutes.
- OK.

1:32:34.376 --> 1:32:35.826
I'm ready.

1:33:41.788 --> 1:33:43.376
Go take a look.

1:33:48.105 --> 1:33:49.313
What do you think?

1:33:49.347 --> 1:33:51.142
How does it look?

1:33:51.177 --> 1:33:53.420
- You look so beautiful.
- Thank you.

1:33:53.455 --> 1:33:55.422
Beautiful!

1:34:00.358 --> 1:34:03.707
Oh, my God,
I'm so happy for you!

1:34:03.741 --> 1:34:06.295
Do you want to get
your hair done, too?

1:34:06.330 --> 1:34:08.401
Can you make it pretty
like Olivia's?

1:34:09.264 --> 1:34:11.059
Of course I can.

1:34:11.093 --> 1:34:13.302
You're very beautiful,
so it's gonna be easy.

1:34:13.337 --> 1:34:14.752
Come on.

1:34:26.833 --> 1:34:27.938
There you go.

1:34:39.535 --> 1:34:42.435
Olivia, you look amazing.

1:34:42.469 --> 1:34:44.989
[Phone beeps]

1:34:45.024 --> 1:34:47.716
Charlie is ready
for the big reveal.

1:34:47.751 --> 1:34:49.856
You want to go see
how he cleans up?

1:34:52.756 --> 1:34:54.102
Got it?

1:35:09.082 --> 1:35:11.360
There you go, now you're ready
to walk down the aisle.

1:35:11.395 --> 1:35:13.259
Thank you.

1:35:17.056 --> 1:35:18.816
Oh, do you know
where the bathroom is?

1:35:18.851 --> 1:35:20.749
Oh, sure.
It's right over there.

1:35:20.784 --> 1:35:22.095
Thanks.

1:35:24.201 --> 1:35:26.237
[Charlie] Do you know
how beautiful you are?

1:35:27.031 --> 1:35:28.550
And how lucky I am?

1:35:28.584 --> 1:35:30.345
Do you know how cold you are?

1:35:31.070 --> 1:35:33.037
Freezing.

1:35:34.556 --> 1:35:36.489
I can't wait to marry you.

1:35:45.084 --> 1:35:46.464
[Knocking on door]

1:35:46.499 --> 1:35:48.052
Hey, they're looking for you.

1:35:48.087 --> 1:35:49.847
Need help with the veil,
I think.

1:35:49.882 --> 1:35:51.469
- On my way.
- OK.

1:36:01.859 --> 1:36:04.793
Oh! Claire, you want to come
over here and help with this,

1:36:04.828 --> 1:36:07.416
so I don't mess up
your beautiful work?

1:36:09.522 --> 1:36:11.041
The usher's here.

1:36:11.075 --> 1:36:14.044
It's time for me to go,
so I'll see you out there?

1:36:14.078 --> 1:36:15.424
Yeah.

1:36:15.459 --> 1:36:17.081
I love you so much.

1:36:17.116 --> 1:36:18.911
I love you, too.

1:36:18.945 --> 1:36:21.051
- OK, baby.
- OK.

1:36:41.381 --> 1:36:43.418
There you go.

1:36:43.452 --> 1:36:45.247
Thanks.

1:36:46.870 --> 1:36:50.977
Sorry that I barked at you
the other day.

1:36:51.012 --> 1:36:54.809
Pressure's just been building
for a while, you know?

1:36:56.224 --> 1:36:57.570
Yes.

1:36:58.260 --> 1:36:59.848
Yes.

1:37:01.643 --> 1:37:03.093
Claire, are you OK?

1:37:07.994 --> 1:37:09.030
No.

1:37:11.308 --> 1:37:13.344
No, I'm sorry.

1:37:16.140 --> 1:37:17.935
I have to tell you something.

1:37:19.143 --> 1:37:20.973
OK.
What is it?

1:37:27.289 --> 1:37:28.532
I don't run.

1:37:30.016 --> 1:37:31.397
What?

1:37:36.160 --> 1:37:38.404
I don't run, Olivia.

1:37:44.651 --> 1:37:46.343
[Sobbing]

1:37:59.943 --> 1:38:01.910
[Man] Here we go.

1:39:07.286 --> 1:39:09.667
[♪ RICHARD WAGNER:
"Bridal Chorus"]

1:40:02.134 --> 1:40:04.032
[Man] Please be seated.

1:40:13.628 --> 1:40:15.078
Baby.

1:40:44.383 --> 1:40:46.488
[Gasping]

1:41:02.228 --> 1:41:03.816
[Screaming]

1:41:09.339 --> 1:41:10.754
What did you do?

1:41:14.758 --> 1:41:15.862
What did you do?

1:41:17.312 --> 1:41:18.865
What's going on?

1:41:18.900 --> 1:41:21.144
Where is she? Where is she?

1:41:36.780 --> 1:41:39.886
[Olivia] 'I mean,
look how amazing we turned out.'
